However, compared to the rest of the world, the situation of improvement especially in the Czech Republic.
According to the World Bank, from the point of view of the conditions for having a company, Czech Republic is in position 74a, that is, eight places worse than last year.
The Absurdity of the Year contest was held for the first time in 2006 and each year is repeated in the same way.
Anyone can indicate any administrative or bureaucratic absurdity each year between April and the end of September, when the competition is closed.
